CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FThe United States has launched fresh
OL,7,Fstrikes against Iran after a drone
OL,8,Fattack targeted a Panama-flagged
OL,9,Fvessel in the Strait of Hormuz on
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,FEarly Sunday, the US military's
OL,13,FCentral Command (CENTCOM) said it
OL,14,Fstruck Iranian military "surveillance
OL,15,Finfrastructure, communication systems,
OL,16,Fair defense sites, drone storage
OL,17,Ffacilities and minelayer capabilities"
OL,18,Fin response to Iran's attack on the
OL,19,Ftanker.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FCENTCOM posted to social media that
OL,7,Fthey has conducted strikes on 10
OL,8,FIranian military targets at "multiple
OL,9,Flocations in and near the Strait of
OL,10,FHormuz".
OL,12,FIran's paramilitary Revolutionary
OL,13,FGuard then launched drone and missile
OL,14,Fattacks Sunday, targeting Bahrain and
OL,15,FKuwait, and threatened a "complete
OL,16,Fhalt" could come to negotiations to
OL,17,Fend the war if Washington continues
OL,18,Fits attacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
