FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FEfforts to reopen the Strait of
OL,7,FHormuz, the narrow mouth of the
OL,8,FPersian Gulf that once carried a fifth
OL,9,Fof the world's oil and natural gas,
OL,10,Fwithout Iran's direct oversight, has
OL,11,Fsparked the crossfire in the region.
OL,13,FA multinational maritime body,
OL,14,Foverseen by the US Navy, said Saturday
OL,15,Fthat it would expand a route near Oman
OL,16,Fin the Strait of Hormuz to allow for
OL,17,Fboth inbound and outbound traffic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Iran says it should have
OL,7,Fsole control over the strait after the
OL,8,Fwar, challenging the long-held view
OL,9,Fthat the waterway is open to all
OL,10,Fcountries, even though it lies within
OL,11,Fthe territorial waters of Iran and
OL,12,FOman.
OL,14,FTehran has twice attacked vessels
OL,15,Fgoing through the Oman route, backed
OL,16,Fby a United Nations agency, in recent
OL,17,Fdays.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
