PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FThe Panamanian-flagged tanker Kiku,
OL,7,Fcarried crude oil for the state-run
OL,8,Fenergy company of Qatar, a key
OL,9,Fnegotiator between Iran and the United
OL,10,FStates.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FIn a social media post, Trump said the
OL,18,FUS had "struck Iranian missile and
OL,19,Fdrone storage locations, and coastal
OL,20,Fradar sites, for violating the Cease
OL,21,FFire Agreement, AGAIN!"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FHe warned of a point where the US may
OL,7,Fno longer be able to be reasonable
OL,8,F"and will be forced to militarily
OL,9,Fcomplete the job."
OL,11,F"If that happens, the Islamic Republic
OL,12,Fof Iran will no longer exist!" Trump
OL,13,Fwrote on Truth Social.
OL,15,FThe incident follows a similar back-
OL,16,Fand-forth that occurred just days
OL,17,Fprior, when an Iranian drone struck a
OL,18,Fmerchant vessel off the coast of Oman
OL,19,Fon Thursday, and the US military
OL,20,Fretaliated with strikes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FAccording to ship-tracking websites,
OL,7,Fthe Kiku left a Qatari oil field in
OL,8,Fthe middle of the Persian Gulf earlier
OL,9,Fin the week and was bound for a port
OL,10,Fin the United Arab Emirates that sits
OL,11,Fon the Gulf of Oman, just on the other
OL,12,Fside of the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FIt appeared to be attempting to use a
OL,15,Froute established near the coast of
OL,16,FOman, serving as an alternative to the
OL,17,Froute sanctioned by Iran that runs
OL,18,Fthrough its own waters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FThe US military said that "Iran had a
OL,7,Fchance to honor the ceasefire
OL,8,Fagreement" but "elected not to" when
OL,9,Fits forces attacked the Kiku.
OL,11,FAfter the US strikes early Sunday,
OL,12,FKuwait's military said air defenses
OL,13,Fintercepted incoming Iranian drones
OL,14,Fand missiles. It offered no immediate
OL,15,Finformation on any damage. Kuwait is
OL,16,Fhome to a major US Army base.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
