FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Bahrain's Foreign Ministry
OL,7,Fissued a statement denouncing what it
OL,8,Fcalled "a dangerous escalation that
OL,9,Freveals that what Tehran is doing is
OL,10,Fnot a passing act, nor an isolated
OL,11,Fincident, but rather a deliberate
OL,12,Fapproach and a systematic pattern of
OL,13,Frepeated aggression against the
OL,14,Fsovereignty of the kingdom, and the
OL,15,Fsecurity of its citizens and
OL,16,Fresidents."
OL,18,FBahrain is home to the U.S. Navy's 5th
OL,19,FFleet, whose base there came under
OL,20,Frepeated attack during the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
