FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1782659892
OL,3,CUS and Iran exchange strikes
OL,4,Cthreatening an end to talks
OL,6,FThe Guard claimed responsibility for
OL,7,Fboth attacks, saying it targeted Al
OL,8,FAsad Air Base in Kuwait.
OL,10,F"Let the enemy know that violating the
OL,11,Fceasefire ... will lead to a complete
OL,12,Fhalt of ongoing processes," the Guard
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FThe Guard, which controls Iran's
OL,16,Fballistic missile arsenal, answers
OL,17,Fonly to Supreme Leader Ayatollah
OL,18,FMojtaba Khamenei and is thought to be
OL,19,Fwielding even greater influence now in
OL,20,Fthe Islamic Republic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
